{"id":469127,"date":[{"year":1965,"month":8,"day":29}],"page":"6","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"","column":"","genre":"木刻","count":"355","ytitle":"","mtitle":"团结人民　教育人民 打击敌人　消灭敌人","ftitle":"","authors":[],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"编后"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在抗日战争时期，抗日根据地的文艺工作者，在毛主席的文艺方针指引下，坚持文艺为无产阶级政治服务，为工农兵服务的正确方向，深入群众、深入火热斗争，积极开展各种文艺活动，充分发挥了文艺的“团结人民、教育人民、打击敌人、消灭敌人”的武器作用。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"本版照片和木刻作品选自正在上海举行的纪念伟大抗日战争胜利二十周年美术和摄影作品展览。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入5号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1965\\08\\658t060101.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgaut>杨涵</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>八路军的文艺工作者深入敌占区画宣传壁画</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入5号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1965\\08\\658t060102.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>沙沟战斗——攻敌堡(木刻)"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"杨涵</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入5号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1965\\08\\658t060103.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgaut>戚单</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>读了书又能写又能算(木刻)"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"戚单</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入5号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1965\\08\\658t060104.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgaut>古元</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>拥护咱们老百姓自己的军队(木刻)"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"古元</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入5号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1965\\08\\658t060105.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgaut>夏风</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>民兵练习射击(木刻)"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夏风</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入5号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1965\\08\\658t060106.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgaut>彦涵</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>开展民兵爆炸运动(年画)"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"彦涵</FONT>"}